{"tid":1892433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道武肺大爆發瘋狂慶祝區####$","createTime":"2020-02-22T13:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T13:58:36.000Z","uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c75e53ec8e48470ab17e612dcace3731230b43dd","tid":1892433,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"北海道昨日亦有未滿10歲和10多歲的小學生兄弟倆確診，令人擔心疫情在學校層面擴散。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，2020年日本東京奧運主辦單位今日表示，為防止新型冠狀病毒疫情擴散，決定把今日的義工訓練延期，<span style=\"color: red;\">重申沒有考慮取消奧運，強調不會影響籌備</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你在何地　若然在札幌可感染我<br />\n假使中招　但求念到隔離怎過<br />\n北海道　武漢其實差不多<br />\n何以賴共換不到好結果<br />\n愛莫能助　病情就似雪花般飛過<br />\n那斷腸地　舊愛新歡也都賴野"},{"pid":"0bdd36a8eae88578d847b168ccae61f375de11b2","tid":1892433,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"起底 &gt; 帶節奏 &gt; 拉"},{"pid":"3b2e8aa0a33a9b8a2c3611065f1220f374907f59","tid":1892433,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}